title: Bruce Springsteen 2005-06-25 , STOCKHOLM
description:
Bruce Sprinsteen solo accoustic in Stockholm 25 june 2005. 

The Rising on disc 1 fades 
after 2 minutes or so. Disc 2 has the complete song. 

Setlist 

DOWNBOUND TRAIN 
REASON TO BELIEVE 
DEVILS AND DUST 
EMPTY SKY 
LONG TIME COMING 
BLACK COWBOYS 
THE PROMISE 
THE RIVER 
PART MAN PART MONKEY 
ALL I'M THINKING ABOUT 
ACROSS THE BORDER 
RENO 
POINT BLANK 
WALK LIKE A MAN 
MY HOMETOWN 
THE RISING 
LUCKY TOWN 
JESUS WAS AN ONLY SON 
THIS HARD LAND 
THE HITTER 
MATAMOROS BANKS 

CADILLAC RANCH - RAMROD 
BOBBY JEAN 
BLINDED BY THE LIGHT 
THE PROMISED LAND 
DREAM BABY DREAM 

Sound is great. One of the best from this tour. 

And no music from the PA system on this recording.
